I had this problem a while ago, this is the feedback I got from ETS.

Try following these steps

1) Restore old YouTube (from the pull down of your avatar)

2) Pull down from your avatar again, and select "see more" or "more account" (not sure of the exact words)

3) There should be two different berkeley.edu accounts, please try selecting another one and reload the lecture again.
